292
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:11,210
What should we do?

293
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:21,320
We've been waiting in the cafe
for so long.

294
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:22,840
I suppose the informant

295
00:20:22,937 --> 00:20:24,840
can see our sincerity now.

296
00:20:25,930 --> 00:20:27,080
Yeah.

297
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:28,760
Email him.

298
00:20:35,170 --> 00:20:36,360
Cafe?

299
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:40,970
There must be something special

300
00:20:40,970 --> 00:20:42,890
around that cafe.

301
00:20:42,982 --> 00:20:44,693
Otherwise, they wouldn't travel so far

302
00:20:44,715 --> 00:20:45,690
just to get coffee.

303
00:20:45,690 --> 00:20:48,040
