and I'll have to clean it up.

371
00:25:24,600 --> 00:25:26,040
Think about something else.

372
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:38,280
Walk in a straight line.

373
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:39,250
Come back.

374
00:25:39,500 --> 00:25:40,690
