- I can.

375
00:25:40,690 --> 00:25:42,471
You can't even get
this simple thing done.

376
00:25:42,970 --> 00:25:44,970
Come on. Ready. Hold tight.

377
00:25:45,840 --> 00:25:46,520
One,

