394
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:43,360
Sir, I'm on duty today.

395
00:26:45,204 --> 00:26:46,170
Carry on with it.

396
00:26:46,410 --> 00:26:47,040
Yes, Sir.

397
00:27:59,210 --> 00:28:00,170
Mr. Han,

398
00:28:00,471 --> 00:28:01,890
