399
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:03,450
They moved to the Aston Hotel.

400
00:28:03,450 --> 00:28:04,650
They changed hotels?

401
00:28:06,970 --> 00:28:08,410
Why?

402
00:28:08,970 --> 00:28:10,040
I found it strange, too.

403
00:28:10,730 --> 00:28:13,650
Aston is the most high-end hotel
in Roman.

404
00:28:13,930 --> 00:28:15,730
Not just anyone can afford
to stay there.

405
00:28:27,490 --> 00:28:28,320
Welcome.

406
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:42,250
Xin.

407
00:28:43,080 --> 00:28:44,410
It's not locked. Come in.

408
00:28:47,970 --> 00:28:49,600
Your room's huge.

409
00:28:50,080 --> 00:28:51,170
Not bad.

410
00:28:52,410 --> 00:28:53,320
Why?

411
00:28:53,490 --> 00:28:54,410
