440
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:29,450
Eat it here, okay?

441
00:30:29,450 --> 00:30:30,170
Okay.

442
00:31:03,210 --> 00:31:03,840
Thank you.

443
00:31:22,650 --> 00:31:24,210
Let's head over there for today.

444
00:31:24,730 --> 00:31:25,250
Right.

445
00:31:25,280 --> 00:31:27,210
Later, I'll go to the cafe,

446
00:31:27,250 --> 00:31:28,170
