504
00:35:31,560 --> 00:35:34,410
Fleet Commander, Xu Jianhua.

505
00:35:34,560 --> 00:35:36,720
Political Commissar, Song Guoqing.

506
00:35:38,450 --> 00:35:39,200
Comrades,

507
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:41,410
