- Let's go, Dad.

553
00:41:39,770 --> 00:41:40,410
Mr. Han.

554
00:41:40,940 --> 00:41:41,560
I'm here.

555
00:41:44,370 --> 00:41:45,040
Mr. Han,

556
00:41:45,890 --> 00:41:47,970
