00:42:27,970 --> 00:42:29,080
They went to the 41st floor.

572
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,370
I didn't dare follow too closely,

573
00:42:30,560 --> 00:42:33,640
so I don't know which room exactly.

574
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,370
Maybe

575
00:42:37,450 --> 00:42:38,520
we should try our luck.

576
00:42:51,381 --> 00:42:54,861
♪The vast sky and sea,
this deep blue expanse♪

577
00:42:55,551 --> 00:42:58,821
♪So deep, so boundless♪

578
00:42:59,161 --> 00:43:02,331
♪Just like your arms♪

579
00:43:02,821 --> 00:43:05,941
♪Shielding me from the dark clouds♪

580
00:43:06,231 --> 00:43:09,871
♪Always bearing it all in silence♪

581
00:43:09,871 --> 00:43:16,291
♪Even the long, long road gives me peace
when you're there♪

582
00:43:16,791 --> 00:43:21,191
♪Not one to show romance
in front of others♪

583
00:43:21,651 --> 00:43:24,741
♪You speak of dreams
with such calm simplicity♪

584
00:43:25,531 --> 00:43:30,331
♪But I know your heart
holds much deeper hopes♪

585
00:43:32,601 --> 00:43:34,441
♪I truly understand♪

586
00:43:34,931 --> 00:43:39,121
♪You speak of love so slowly♪

587
00:43:39,371 --> 00:43:45,341
♪But your eyes have already
told me everything♪

588
00:43:45,847 --> 00:43:48,537
♪Using up all my fortune♪

589
00:43:48,541 --> 00:43:52,941
♪Just to trade a lifetime with you♪

590
00:43:53,031 --> 00:43:55,251
♪Thank you for awakening♪

591
00:43:55,261 --> 00:44:00,341
♪The courage once hidden in my fear♪

592
00:44:00,481 --> 00:44:03,671
♪Turning every chance into certainty♪

593
00:44:04,001 --> 00:44:07,531
♪Turning every tie into companionship♪

594
00:44:07,611 --> 00:44:12,581
♪Blooming into brilliance
for all the years to come♪

595
00:44:12,581 --> 00:44:16,571
♪No one can tear us apart♪

596
00:44:16,761 --> 00:44:20,111
♪Each time my palm feels warmth again♪

597
00:44:20,371 --> 00:44:25,711
♪The memories return,
and I'm no longer alone♪

598
00:44:26,601 --> 00:44:30,591
♪No matter how far
across time and space♪

599
00:44:30,841 --> 00:44:34,241
♪My longing reaches you in silence♪

600
00:44:34,361 --> 00:44:38,891
♪No need to call out loudly♪

601
00:44:38,891 --> 00:44:41,561
♪No matter how much it takes♪

602
00:44:41,581 --> 00:44:45,991
♪To bring this drifting heart to shore♪

603
00:44:45,991 --> 00:44:49,251
♪Thank you for standing behind me♪

604
00:44:49,271 --> 00:44:53,321
♪Lighting up the darkness and despair♪

605
00:44:53,321 --> 00:44:56,791
♪The bigger the world,
the lonelier it feels♪

606
00:44:56,791 --> 00:45:00,561
♪Only by your side♪

607
00:45:00,571 --> 00:45:07,651
♪Can I truly feel this warmth inside♪
